---
---
<section class="demo-napsack" id="demo-carousel">
  <div class="container--wide">
    <p class="section-label fade-up">NAPSack</p>
    <h2 class="fade-up">Labeling Interaction Data</h2>
    <p class="demo-napsack__intro fade-up">
      NAPSack is a lightweight, passive tool for collecting labeled interaction data at scale. It continuously records screenshots, groups interactions into bursts of adjacent events, compresses via heuristic filtering (reducing storage by approximately 70% without compromising quality), and annotates the resulting records with a VLM. We apply NAPSack to the Screenomics dataset, labeling over 360K actions across a month of continuous phone usage from 20 users (1.8K hours of screen time). Below, watch a labeled session play back.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="napsack-player fade-up" id="napsack-player">
    <div class="napsack-layout">
      <div class="napsack-video-col">
        <div class="napsack-segments" id="napsack-segments">
          <!-- Segment tabs injected by JS -->
        </div>
        <div class="napsack-viewport">
          <video
            class="napsack-video"
            id="napsack-video"
            muted
            playsinline
          ></video>

          <div class="napsack-controls">
            <button class="napsack-btn" id="napsack-playpause" aria-label="Play/Pause">
              <svg class="icon-play" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"/></svg>
              <svg class="icon-pause" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="display:none"><rect x="6" y="4" width="4" height="16"/><rect x="14" y="4" width="4" height="16"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="napsack-progress-wrap" id="napsack-progress-wrap">
              <div class="napsack-progress-bar" id="napsack-progress-bar"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="napsack-labels-col">
        <h4 class="napsack-labels-title">Labeled Actions</h4>
        <div class="napsack-label-stack" id="napsack-label-stack">
          <!-- Cards managed by JS -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .demo-napsack {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .demo-napsack__intro {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .napsack-player {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .napsack-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .napsack-video-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .napsack-labels-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .napsack-labels-title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .napsack-segments {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .napsack-segments :global(button) {
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-tertiary);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .napsack-segments :global(button:hover) {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .napsack-segments :global(button.active) {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .napsack-viewport {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-text);
  }

  .napsack-video {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 960 / 624;
    object-fit: cover;
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .napsack-controls {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
  }

  .napsack-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .napsack-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .napsack-progress-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 3px;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
  }

  .napsack-progress-bar {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 3px;
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.1s linear;
  }

  .napsack-label-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  /* Cards are created by JS, so they need :global to bypass Astro scoping */
  .napsack-label-stack :global(.napsack-label-card) {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    transition: background 2.4s ease, opacity 1.5s ease, transform 1.5s ease, margin-top 1.5s ease;
  }

  .napsack-label-stack :global(.napsack-label-card.active) {
    background: rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.25);
  }

  .napsack-label-stack :global(.napsack-label-text) {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .napsack-label-stack :global(.napsack-label-time) {
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .napsack-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .napsack-segments :global(button) {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    }
    .napsack-labels-title {
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>

<script src="../scripts/carousel.js"></script>
